val rawData = sc.textFile("dataset")
  
  rawData.first
  
  case class DSet(c1: Int,c2:Int,c3:Int,c4:Int,c5:Int,c6:Int,c7:Int,c8:Int,c9:Int,c10:Int)
  val dataset = spark.read.text("dataset").map(row => row(0).toString.split(",")).map(row => DSet(row(0).toInt,row(1).toInt,row(2).toInt,row(3).toInt,row(4).toInt,row(5).toInt,row(6).toInt,row(7).toInt,row(8).toInt,row(9).toInt))
  
  //dataset.first
  
  dataset.registerTempTable("data_set")

%sql
select c1, sum(c2) from data_set group by c1 order by sum(c2) desc

case class Status(code: String, message: String)
case class Result(sessionCode:String,symbol:String,tickPrice:String,tickSize:String,timestamp:String,tradingDay:String)
case class Ticker(status: Status, results: Array[Result])
val dataset = spark.read.json("getHistoryUSFuturesTick.json").as[Ticker]

val ticks = dataset.flatMap(t => t.results)

ticks.head(10)
ticks.registerTempTable("ticks")
